         <abstract id="aspace_d3d5a27e6a641576bd7561997215669c">Contains letters from T. S. Eliot to various individuals, drafts of writings by Eliot, and writings on Eliot by Helen Gardner. Portions of the collection are photocopies and photostats of material held by other repositories.</abstract>
